SELECT orderlines[0].* FROM orders WHERE test_id="select_func" ORDER BY orderlines[0].productId, orderlines[0].qty
SELECT orderlines[0].*, orderlines[1].* FROM orders WHERE test_id="select_func" ORDER BY orderlines[0].productId, orderlines[1].productId
SELECT orderlines[0].*, id, orderlines[1].* FROM orders WHERE test_id="select_func" ORDER BY orderlines[0].productId, id
SELECT orderlines[0].productId.* FROM orders WHERE test_id="select_func" ORDER BY orderlines[0].productId
SELECT custId, orderlines[1].* FROM orders WHERE test_id="select_func" ORDER BY custId
